{
  "stem": "280.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was-- a lot among them, very well-to-do, with very elegant people, big businesses, big-name businesses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they had their own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had their own.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the Orthodox, and they had their own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] how old?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war-- well, of course I was aware of the war from-- I read newspapers from a very, very young age.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were always hoping-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a kind of hope that-- that the-- the-- the-- the Germans are going to-- are not going to succeed, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- we are-- they are going to win, and everything is going to be fine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although it was, I guess, in 1942-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 1940-- let-- let me-- let me backtrack a little.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I went to [ROMANIAN] and I was in fifth grade, I-- then already the Germans were taking over-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] taking over Czechoslovakia and Europe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, it reverberated in Romania also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they brought in some laws, which were not-- not existing before, that in the high schools-- in the [ROMANIAN], which was the state school, they didn't allow only a certain percentage of Jews-- 6% for a couple of years and a couple of year later none.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So of course, that touched my life already because I couldn't go on any further.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this point, I-- I started school at seven, 11, I had to be about 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that disrupted my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would have gone on to school, and I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it disrupted-- but the whole Jewish life was disrupted, not only my life personally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but again, as I tell you, there were shortages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were-- there were terrible rumors.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
